ailed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sev1665703532366.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sev1665703532366.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sev1665703532366.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sev1665703532366\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Settings: Message Frame\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether the <code class=\"ph codeph\">clrmess</code> ProcScript instruction is enabled or disabled, and whether application messages are sent to the application's message frame or to the application's transcript window.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sev1665703532366__section_w1442ab1b7b1_w1443ab1b7_w1444ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sev1665703532366__section_jrs_54h_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d933987e63\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"sev1665703532366__ul_k4y_v4h_tcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sev1665703532366__li_d53609e1_d53610e1_d53611e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dit1665703532527.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dit1665703532527.html\" title=\"Determine whether the clrmess ProcScript instruction is enabled.\">ProcScript instruction clrmess</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sev1665703532366__li_d53612e1_d53613e1_d53614e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xsr1665703532612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xsr1665703532612.html\" title=\"Specify where messages are sent if the $PUTMESS_LOG_FILE assignment setting is not specified.\">Send messages to</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ibc1665703531301.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Settings: I/O Print</a><p>Choose the level of I/O messages that are displayed in the message frame or transcript window.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yno1665703531917.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Settings: Triggers</a><p>Choose the triggers you want to be enabled or disabled for debugging, or those that you want to be set as breakpoints.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ppp1665703531653.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Settings: Tracing</a><p>Choose the level or type of ProcScript-related tracing to be displayed in the message frame or transcript window.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uha1665703532184.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Settings: Errors</a><p>Set a specific ProcScript error value ($procerror) as a breakpoint.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8422676\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up